<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        button[type="submit"]{
            width : 200px;
            height : 100px;
            background-color: rgb(170, 214, 228);
            color : black;
            outline : none;
            border : none;
            border-radius : 20px;
            cursor : pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    상품 목록 보여주는 페이지!
    <h1>/:name즉 이름으로 찾는 상품 페이지!</h1>
    <h2>메인 search bar에서 상품 검색 or category로 검색하면 이거 나옴!</h2>
    <a href="http://localhost:3000/item-detail">상품1</a>
    <button type="submit" class="purchase">구매</button>
    <h2>구매를 누르면 ajax로 data보내주기!!</h2>

    <div class="container"></div>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.min.js"></script>
    <script>

        const xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
        const container = document.querySelector('.container');
        xhr.onload = function(){
            if(this.status === 200){
                container.innerHTML = xhr.responseText;
            }else{
                console.warn('안돼1');
            }
        }
        xhr.open('get','./ajax.html');
        xhr.send();
    </script>
</body>
</html>